# Release data source

- `WAGroupManager/package.json` and `WAGroupManager/src/config/changelog.js` are the canonical
  product version and changelog sources.
- `data/releases.json` is generated by the application release workflow. Do not independently
  edit product versions or release notes in this repository.
- The version in this repository's `package.json` belongs to the website tooling and is not the
  GroupWire product version.
- Keep this repository deployable as a standalone Render Static Site. Do not add application
  server code, application secrets, or dependencies on the app's runtime filesystem.
